{"tid":1183712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[純討論]其實唔識教仔真係唔好生仔..","createTime":"2019-06-03T06:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T08:29:51.000Z","uid":46277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d32a4eb04d74fda7f41a6220543ffdf8aa6fb30f","tid":1183712,"uid":46277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟琴日去玩具街買野，買完野就排隊比錢。<br />\n排排下隊，就發現前面突然間滴滴聲，就以為冷氣機滴水啦。<br />\n點知抬頭一望，唔對路，頂你個肺，啲水黃色既？<br />\n原來係前面個9、10歲既細路係到賴尿，仲要好似噴泉⛲️咁 不停賴賴到成個地下都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就梗係嚇到彈起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個職員都嚇左一嚇，問左句：「嘩，小朋友，你賴尿呀？」<br />\n之後個小朋友既呀媽就近乎發癲咁鬧人：「你做咩話我小朋友賴尿呀？你唔可以咁講啲小朋友！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n講完呢句野之後，就拖住個仔，急急腳咁走人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一路行一路賴賴到半條路都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同個職員都嚇到呆左，成件事唔過一分鐘，成分鐘都我都係維持住咁既表情「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，想反應都反應唔切。<br />\n<br />\n事後都同佢職員同老板都傾左兩句，都覺得唔知點解個細路9、10歲，望落個樣正正常常都可以不停噴泉式咁賴都算，個老母仲可以一句唔好意思都冇，聲大夾惡咁屌返人就走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個老母比人一個「我個仔係賴尿，咁又點？我係客，我大曬」既感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬，咁樣點得架... 我真係覺得，呢啲人唔識教仔唔好生，唔好累己累人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85dad8105aa17635d2e74b2687bf3580728c2a8","tid":1183712,"uid":838,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"未必係唔識教，可能係個仔有病控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係個老母無歉意"},{"pid":"94d8674f64bea8cfe672aa35b25057949fa6c3bb","tid":1183712,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"關你叉事<br />\n拖地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f